  "texts": [
    "Based on these two steps, ACOS quadruples can be extracted from each review sentence.",
    "Table 8 shows that DP-ACOS achieves the lowest performance.",
    "The limitations of DP-ACOS are as follows:",
    "• Dependence on rules and lexicons: DP-ACOS relies on rules and lexicons for its performance, which may limit its accuracy if the rules and lexicons do not cover all cases.",
    "• Limited suitability for new domains: DP-ACOS requires pre-labelled aspect category information in the training set."
